  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to assess the validity of a relaxation app. This will be accomplished by
      obtaining self-report measures about mood and respiratory symptoms. We hypothesize that
      self-report in the relaxation app condition will be different from that of the relaxation
      only condition.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
